<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.8.9">
<l>koḷvaṉāṉ māvali mūvaṭi tāveṉṟa</l>
<l>kaḷvaṉē kañcaṉai vañcittu vāṇaṉai</l>
<l>yuḷvaṉmai tīravō rāyiran tōṭṭuṇitta</l>
<l>puḷvallā yuṉṉai yeññāṉṟu poruntuvaṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I take. O robber who said to Māvali “give [me]</l>
<l>three steps”, you who, having deceived Kamsa,</l>
<l>cut off the one thousand arms of Bāṇa so that [his] inner strength ended,</l>
<l>you who master the bird, when shall I join you?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
